# 🏗️ Architecture Rules: findy.place

## 1. Architectural Pattern (Feature-Sliced Design)

You are a Software Architect. This project uses strict Next.js 16+ (App Router). The structure is divided by business domains (Features). The core product is a **place-centric** discovery app: the atomic unit is always a `Place`, never a raw post or video.

```
src/
├── app/                              # Routing ONLY
│   ├── layout.tsx                    # Minimal root layout (no html/body — delegated to [locale])
│   ├── [locale]/                     # i18n — ALL pages live here
│   │   ├── layout.tsx                # Locale layout: html lang, fonts, NextIntlClientProvider
│   │   ├── page.tsx                  # Homepage / hero search
│   │   ├── explore/                  # Main discovery experience
│   │   │   ├── layout.tsx            # List + map split layout
