### Placement Rules

| Concern | Where it lives |
|---|---|
| Page routing / layout | `src/app/` |
| Place business logic, UI | `src/features/places/` |
| Semantic search + AI chat | `src/features/search/` |
| Map rendering (client-heavy) | `src/features/map/` |
| Apify ingest + resolve pipeline | `src/features/ingestion/services/` |
| External service clients | `src/lib/` |
| Generic reusable UI primitives | `src/components/ui/` |
| Global shared types | `src/types/` |

